{"tid":320011,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[世上只有一個林鄭！] 廁紙網站惡搞林鄭　巫堃泰被廉署邀協助調查","createTime":"2017-07-13T08:27:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-27T18:20:14.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"0a99b966c49ca0d8e96e4911c197994939139f95","tid":320011,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T08:27:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/廁紙網站惡搞林鄭-巫堃泰被廉署邀協助調查/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E5%BB%81%E7%B4%99%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99%E6%83%A1%E6%90%9E%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD-%E5%B7%AB%E5%A0%83%E6%B3%B0%E8%A2%AB%E5%BB%89%E7%BD%B2%E9%82%80%E5%8D%94%E5%8A%A9%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5%2F&d=CcwWB%2B7%2BJiuzxBP24F9pksmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=6591e4a4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E5%BB%81%E7%B4%99%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99%E6%83%A1%E6%90%9E%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD-%E5%B7%AB%E5%A0%83%E6%B3%B0%E8%A2%AB%E5%BB%89%E7%BD%B2%E9%82%80%E5%8D%94%E5%8A%A9%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5%2F&h=1408bce1\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/廁紙網站惡搞林鄭-巫堃泰被廉署邀協助調查/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/mo-01_UwRuV_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fmo-01_UwRuV_1200x0.png&h=0448bcbc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今年一月，社運人士巫堃泰疑創立惡搞網站「<a href=\"http://carrielam2017.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcarrielam2017.hk&d=CcwWB%2B7%2BJiuzxBP24F9pksmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=2516974e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">carrielam2017.hk</a>」，網頁內只顯示了一卷廁紙，諷刺林鄭月娥的「廁紙門」事件。巫堃泰今日於Facebook稱收到廉署電話，稱希望他協助調查有關網頁為公職選舉而招致選舉開支。<br />\n<br />\n巫堃泰今日在Facebook寫道，下午有廉署調查人員致電他，<a href=\"http://希望他協助調查有關網域名carrielam.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E5%B8%8C%E6%9C%9B%E4%BB%96%E5%8D%94%E5%8A%A9%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5%E6%9C%89%E9%97%9C%E7%B6%B2%E5%9F%9F%E5%90%8Dcarrielam.hk&d=CcwWB%2B7%2BJiuzxBP24F9pksmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=1d066f59\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">希望他協助調查有關網域名carrielam.hk</a>及四張於網站展示的相片，為一場公職選舉而招致選舉開支。巫堃泰認為國際人權公約及《香港人權法》均保障港人表達自由，<a href=\"http://又指與carrielam.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E5%8F%88%E6%8C%87%E8%88%87carrielam.hk&d=CcwWB%2B7%2BJiuzxBP24F9pksmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=2747b30b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">又指與carrielam.hk</a>域名相同稱呼的人，可謂恆河沙數。<br />\n<br />\n他指廉政公署自梁振英成為特首後便被受指責，「我不希望本次事件是另一宗政治調查，令署方與打壓表達自由甚至白色恐怖扯上關係」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://今年一月carrielam.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E4%BB%8A%E5%B9%B4%E4%B8%80%E6%9C%88carrielam.hk&d=CcwWB%2B7%2BJiuzxBP24F9pksmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=6414d7d1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">今年一月carrielam.hk</a>的網站於網上廣傳，內容只有一頁，就是一大卷廁紙，似是有心人諷刺林鄭的廁紙門醜聞。《立場新聞》記者翻查資料，發現該網的擁有人是巫堃泰。<br />\n<br />\n巫堃泰於香港大學修讀法律系碩士課程，去年參選校務委員會研究生代表選舉，他現在亦是「立言香港」的委員之一。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg3-2.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-0/p296x100/19989525_1405326462837064_3706319029262975041_n.png?oh=d4e3ee3a993e3788e1d900c20eb92e0d&amp;oe=5A1137B9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkg3-2.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-0%2Fp296x100%2F19989525_1405326462837064_3706319029262975041_n.png%3Foh%3Dd4e3ee3a993e3788e1d900c20eb92e0d%26oe%3D5A1137B9&h=68ab48c3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1c4e15518612e93b21a5ed10980737a9ab969062","tid":320011,"uid":62532,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T08:30:45.000Z","msg":"老廉都開始唔廉啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁撚多地盤site agent賣鐵袋錢唔捉<br />\n咁撚多公開招標內定sub仔唔捉<br />\n咁多差佬問公器私用唔捉<br />\n捉人開網站諷刺政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67799340f32dfe6fd3a8504dc4fbaf7efcb2221b","tid":320011,"uid":41508,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T08:35:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"10b7811f7672c5e9686754b3a9bab57c9f8adb9b",